# settled_basic.algo.ct
# Algorithm framing for the Settled proof-boundary aggregator.
#
# Scope:
#   Bounded positional-certificate CTS for the 38 representative Settled
#   aggregator fixtures and the malformed/trailing samples exercised by
#   tests/test_settled.c.
#
# Program:
#   Production i emits 1 followed by the six-bit binary index i. During the
#   first input-length steps, every head bit equal to 1 appends the certificate
#   for that input position. Head bit 0 appends nothing. The test harness runs
#   exactly input_length steps and compares the remaining tape with the expected
#   positional certificate, then separately decodes the family/subcase payload
#   and checks the Settled projection semantics.
